<div class="column6">

<h2> 1 </h2>

<p>The main goal of the game is survive. You can move your character with the WASD keys. Make sure not to get too close to enemies because they might notice you! </p>

<h2> 2 </h2>

<p> You can gather materials by getting closer to resources and moving your cursor to it. Press the left mouse button and hold it for a few seconds in order to start gathering materials! </p>

<h2> 3 </h2>

<p> You can access your inventory by pressing the E key. The top right row is your hot bar and you can quickly switch through items by moving your mouse scroll. </p>

</div>

<div class="column7"> 

<img src="Media/4.jpg" width="70px" height="70px" alt = "Intruction1" title = "Instruction1" id="ins1">

<img src="Media/5.jpg" width="70px" height="70px" alt = "Intruction2" title = "Instruction2">

<img src="Media/6.jpg" width="70px" height="70px" alt = "Intruction2" title = "Instruction2">

</div>

<div class="column8"> 

<h2> 4 </h2>

<p> You can gather items by moving on top of it. Same kinds of items can be stacked in order not to consume too much inventory space. </p>

<h2> 5 </h2>

<p> When you have enough materials, it`s time to craft some items. Press the C key and the crafting interface will appear. Switch between crafting recipes and press E once you are ready to craft it.</p>

<h2> 6 </h2>

<p> Once you have proper gear, head over to one of the enemies and get closer to it. When you are close enough you can press your left mouse key and you will start attacking it! Make sure to move and dodge it`s attacks!  </p>

</div>


